window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>He'd never known temptation...until he met her.</p> <p>Alaric lives only for one thing: to fulfill his duty as crown prince of Aurum.</p> <p>It was never a problem until he snuck into a human bar on the eve of his betrothal, and met her. The woman who smacked his hand when he tried to steal her food. The woman who was as strong as any dragon he’d ever met.</p> <p>He didn’t expect to form a bond with her after just one night together. A bond he will have to break to marry his betrothed and fulfill his duty as crown prince.</p> <p>If you want romance, laugh-out-loud moments, and spice, then <i>A Heart of Gold</i> is your perfect fantasy escape.</p> <p>Listen for:</p> <p></p> <ul> <li>Prince Charming, if you always wanted him to sweep you off your feet and rip your shirt off</li> <li>Soulmates</li> <li>Dragons who rule the world</li> </ul> <p><i>A Heart of Gold</i> is Book One in the Dragon Prince’s Mate Series. Alaric and Anastasia’s story is told in this book, and they will get their HEA. The series will continue with Alaric's brothers, and each book can be listened to as a standalone.</p>"; 
